OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,FWatch as UTV asked parents and young
OL,7,Fpeople in Belfast what they thought of
OL,8,Fthe proposed social media ban.
OL,10,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has
OL,11,Fwelcomed the announcement of a social
OL,12,Fmedia ban for under-16s as "the right
OL,13,Fthing to do".
OL,15,FHowever, First Minister Michelle
OL,16,FO'Neill questioned the timing of the
OL,17,Fannoucement and described the issue as
OL,18,Fa "complex conversation".
OL,26,@tD@\OUuD@LO]zD@COUzD@XO]
