OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister announced the
OL,7,Frestriction on Monday as he warned
OL,8,Fsocial media was having an impact on
OL,9,Fchildren's happiness and mental health.
OL,11,FSir Keir said he would not compromise
OL,12,Fon the "safety and happiness of our
OL,13,Fchildren".
OL,15,FHe said he was confident the ban can
OL,16,Fbe effective but acknowledged some
OL,17,Fchildren would find their way around
OL,18,Fit.
OL,20,FThe measure is expected to come into
OL,21,Fforce by early 2027.
OL,26,@tD@HOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
