OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,FPaul Givan said it followed on from
OL,7,Fhis work, such as a pilot programme on
OL,8,Fmobile phone pouches for school pupils
OL,9,Fto leave their devices in during the
OL,10,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
