OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,F"This will take it to the next stage
OL,7,Fthough for broader society, having a
OL,8,Fsocial media restriction in place for
OL,9,Four young people is the right thing to
OL,10,Fdo because of the harm that it causes
OL,11,Fin so many areas around anxiety,
OL,12,Fmental health, depression, low self-
OL,13,Festeem, eating disorders, many caused
OL,14,Fby young people getting access to this
OL,15,Ftechnology much too early, even before
OL,16,Fthey are 10-years-old," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
