PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,FMr Givan said he had spoken to Ben
OL,7,FCarroll, deputy premier of Victoria,
OL,8,FAustralia, where a similar ban has
OL,9,Fbeen introduced, who he said had
OL,10,Fcalled the action "transformative" and
OL,11,Fhaving made a positive impact.
OL,13,F"There will be many parents across
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland who will be saying
OL,15,Fthe Prime Minister is right ` I am one
OL,16,Fof them," he said.
OL,26,@rD@SOUrD@bO]uD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
