PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,F"I know what it is like to have this
OL,7,Fconstant battle about how often your
OL,8,Fphone is being used because I can see
OL,9,Fthe harm that it causes to many of our
OL,10,Fyoung people, and therefore this will
OL,11,Fhelp parents, it will help protect our
OL,12,Fchildren so that we get the right
OL,13,Fapproaches for our young people and we
OL,14,Fdon't rob them of their childhood
OL,15,Fbecause of the harmful nature of
OL,16,Fsocial media."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, First Minister Michelle
OL,19,FO'Neill queried whether the move was
OL,20,F"about internal Labour Party politics
OL,21,Fas opposed to the right thing".
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@NO]|D@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,F"I find it really interesting that
OL,7,FKeir Starmer decides to announce this
OL,8,Fthis morning, in a week that the
OL,9,FMakerfield by-election is going to
OL,10,Fhappen, the week that potentially a
OL,11,Fcontender for the leadership of the
OL,12,FLabour Party is going to come forward,
OL,13,Fand he seems to have rushed forward
OL,14,Fwith this announcement," she told
OL,15,Freporters.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,F"Obviously, we all want to protect our
OL,7,Fchildren, but I think this is allowing
OL,8,Fsocial media companies to get away in
OL,9,Fthe smoke in terms of their
OL,10,Fresponsibility around stuff that they
OL,11,Fallow to be on platforms.
OL,13,F"So I think that this is a very
OL,14,Fcomplex conversation that we need to
OL,15,Fhave a discussion on, and I feel like
OL,16,Fthe announcement this morning has come
OL,17,Fas a direct result of internal Labour
OL,18,FParty politics as opposed to what is
OL,19,Fthe right thing to do in this space."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
