PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781722095
OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Commissioner for
OL,7,FChildren and Young People said he
OL,8,Frecognised the "urgent need for
OL,9,Fmeaningful action to protect children
OL,10,Fonline".
OL,12,FHowever, Chris Quinn added that the
OL,13,Fban "allows the root causes of harm to
OL,14,Fpersist".
OL,16,FHe said that the ban risks "letting
OL,17,Ftechnology companies off the hook" by
OL,18,Fplacing responsibility onto children
OL,19,Fand families.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
