OL,3,C'Social media ban for under-16s 'the
OL,4,Cright thing to do,' Givan says
OL,6,FMr Quinn said the ban could shift
OL,7,Fyoung people's online activity
OL,8,F"towards less regulated, more opaque
OL,9,Fonline spaces.
